  "content": "<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-117.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>第二次去<a href=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/2024/11/05/eastern-beach/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Eastern Beach</a>。同一天内上午去了<a href=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/2024/11/11/cockle-bay-reserve/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cockle Bay</a>海滩，下午又换了一个海滩。夏天日光长，跟很多人一样，在海边享受阳光。而且家里很热，下水比较凉快。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-116.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
